post_text: Homecoming and Red Ribbon Week back-to-back has made for a wild ride up here on the hill, but our teachers have made it!! Thank you to the teachers who have participated in all of the dress up days, spirit days, and door decoration contest! These pictures will be up for public voting until Sunday evening, and then the winner will be announced! Thank you to all of the parents and teachers in the district who have made these last two weeks memorable for our students!

post_text:
Hey guys! I hope everyone has had a great summer break and is ready to get back to work soon. We will be having our first Student Council Meeting on Friday, August 24. I posted previously that this meeting will be at 10:00am, but in order for us to take care of STUCO business and deliver teacher textbooks, I'm asking that STUCO members show up between 8:30 and 9:00am. You will deliver textbooks until 10:00, and then we will have a one hour meeting. Please spread the word to your StuCo friends who have not joined the Facebook page! I look forward to seeing all of you next week!

Mrs. Farmer :)
